WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.609
(soft music)

2
00:00:12.637 --> 00:00:14.377
<v ->What if, like a child, you could simply</v>

3
00:00:14.377 --> 00:00:17.277
call on invisible friends, many call them angels,

4
00:00:17.277 --> 00:00:19.416
and have them help you with anything you wish

5
00:00:19.416 --> 00:00:20.537
throughout your day?

6
00:00:20.537 --> 00:00:22.987
Sounds silly to some, but not to me.

7
00:00:22.987 --> 00:00:26.496
Jean Slatter, a naturopathic physician by profession,

8
00:00:26.496 --> 00:00:28.555
learned of the magic in this process

9
00:00:28.555 --> 00:00:30.496
and has written a wonderful little book titled

10
00:00:30.496 --> 00:00:32.286
Hiring the Heavens.

11
00:00:46.656 --> 00:00:48.836
Jean, I have to tell you, I love your book.

12
00:00:48.836 --> 00:00:51.295
This is one of the most wonderful little books,

13
00:00:51.295 --> 00:00:53.656
and for me, because of my own background

14
00:00:53.656 --> 00:00:55.155
over the last 20 or 30 years,

15
00:00:55.155 --> 00:00:57.296
I've been working with these principles a long time,

16
00:00:57.296 --> 00:01:01.015
but I believe that you have put it in a way

17
00:01:01.015 --> 00:01:04.656
that is not only just accessible to everyone,

18
00:01:04.656 --> 00:01:07.236
but joyful, and even more so,

19
00:01:07.236 --> 00:01:10.316
allows for a higher degree of effectiveness.

20
00:01:10.316 --> 00:01:12.734
And I say that, because hear of law of attraction,

21
00:01:12.734 --> 00:01:14.734
the Secret, all these things have been out there,

22
00:01:14.734 --> 00:01:16.155
but I think that what you've done

23
00:01:16.155 --> 00:01:18.334
is actually much more effective than these,

24
00:01:18.334 --> 00:01:20.615
and you may have heard that from other people.

25
00:01:20.615 --> 00:01:22.335
Why might this be the case?

26
00:01:22.335 --> 00:01:23.435
<v ->Oh, well, thank you, Regina.</v>

27
00:01:23.435 --> 00:01:26.134
You know, I didn't even know

28
00:01:26.134 --> 00:01:28.455
about the law of attraction when I started writing

29
00:01:28.455 --> 00:01:29.874
Hiring the Heavens.

30
00:01:30.614 --> 00:01:32.155
It was my developmental editor

31
00:01:32.155 --> 00:01:34.174
that told me about Abraham-Hicks,

32
00:01:34.174 --> 00:01:37.235
and I started learning more about the law of attraction,

33
00:01:37.235 --> 00:01:39.215
and as the years have gone by,

34
00:01:39.215 --> 00:01:43.355
I began to see how different Hiring the Heavens is

35
00:01:43.355 --> 00:01:45.752
from the law of attraction.

36
00:01:45.752 --> 00:01:47.672
And I really want to bring that out to people,

37
00:01:47.672 --> 00:01:50.052
because I believe it's time

38
00:01:50.052 --> 00:01:53.631
that we know more about another law,

39
00:01:53.631 --> 00:01:55.252
which I call the law of grace.

40
00:01:55.252 --> 00:01:57.131
And it's like two different classrooms.

41
00:01:57.131 --> 00:01:58.512
You can have a classroom

42
00:01:58.512 --> 00:01:59.991
where you learn mathematics

43
00:01:59.991 --> 00:02:01.932
and you can have a classroom where you learn English.

44
00:02:01.932 --> 00:02:03.731
One doesn't negate the other,

45
00:02:03.731 --> 00:02:06.531
but they are definitely two different subjects.

46
00:02:06.531 --> 00:02:08.811
There's the subject of the law of attraction

47
00:02:08.811 --> 00:02:11.691
and then there's the subject of the law of grace,

48
00:02:11.691 --> 00:02:13.292
and what Hiring the Heavens does

49
00:02:13.292 --> 00:02:17.531
is very gently move you into the law of grace,

50
00:02:17.531 --> 00:02:19.708
and here's the difference, okay?

51
00:02:19.708 --> 00:02:20.329
<v Regina>Mmm hmm.</v>

52
00:02:20.329 --> 00:02:22.388
<v ->With the law of attraction,</v>

53
00:02:22.388 --> 00:02:25.488
it requires so much hypervigilance.

54
00:02:25.488 --> 00:02:27.348
You have to do it right.

55
00:02:27.348 --> 00:02:29.989
You have to be,

56
00:02:29.989 --> 00:02:32.689
have enough emotion in your asking,

57
00:02:32.689 --> 00:02:33.305
you have to--

58
00:02:33.305 --> 00:02:33.944
<v Regina>Clarity.</v>

59
00:02:33.944 --> 00:02:34.865
<v ->Clarity!</v>

60
00:02:34.865 --> 00:02:37.485
You have to, I don't use the word "want,"

61
00:02:37.485 --> 00:02:39.644
because that gives you more of wanting,

62
00:02:39.644 --> 00:02:41.424
and stated in the present tense,

63
00:02:41.424 --> 00:02:42.260
and make sure you have enough

64
00:02:42.260 --> 00:02:46.061
attitude of gratitude, and the list goes on and on,

65
00:02:46.061 --> 00:02:48.480
and it makes you become very hypervigiliant.

66
00:02:48.480 --> 00:02:51.441
With this idea of Hiring the Heavens

67
00:02:51.441 --> 00:02:54.401
and the law of grace, you'll soon see

68
00:02:54.401 --> 00:02:56.401
that none of that is required.

69
00:02:56.401 --> 00:03:00.268
As a matter of fact, there's nothing you can do,

70
00:03:00.737 --> 00:03:01.898
and that's the operative word here.

71
00:03:01.898 --> 00:03:05.138
There's nothing you can do to earn this gift.

72
00:03:05.138 --> 00:03:07.838
This gift is given to you by grace

73
00:03:07.838 --> 00:03:12.238
and it doesn't require any amount of time in prayer,

74
00:03:12.238 --> 00:03:14.537
any amount of time in meditation.

75
00:03:14.537 --> 00:03:17.198
It doesn't require that you ask it just right.

76
00:03:17.198 --> 00:03:20.678
It doesn't require that you have an attitude of gratitude.

77
00:03:20.678 --> 00:03:23.658
None of those things are requirements at all.

78
00:03:23.658 --> 00:03:25.518
In fact, there's nothing you can do to earn it

79
00:03:25.518 --> 00:03:27.178
and there's nothing that you can do

80
00:03:27.178 --> 00:03:28.817
to have it taken away from you.

81
00:03:28.817 --> 00:03:30.658
It's a gift of grace.

82
00:03:30.658 --> 00:03:33.737
And this is really important because

83
00:03:33.737 --> 00:03:36.137
I know that there are many clients I've worked with,

84
00:03:36.137 --> 00:03:38.677
and I'm sure that you've worked with, as well,

85
00:03:38.677 --> 00:03:41.827
who have some very dire circumstances

86
00:03:41.827 --> 00:03:44.087
and sad circumstances

87
00:03:44.087 --> 00:03:45.808
where there may have been abuse

