00:04:02.115 --> 00:04:04.875
is just salt in the wound.

96
00:04:04.875 --> 00:04:08.754
And it's a bitter pill that, at that time,

97
00:04:08.754 --> 00:04:10.474
that person just cannot handle.

98
00:04:10.474 --> 00:04:12.115
<v Regina>Because it's more disempowering</v>

99
00:04:12.115 --> 00:04:12.994
to the situation.

100
00:04:12.994 --> 00:04:14.135
<v ->It really is.</v>

101
00:04:14.135 --> 00:04:14.735
<v Regina>Yeah.</v>

102
00:04:14.735 --> 00:04:17.975
<v ->What Hiring the Heavens does, in a very light way,</v>

103
00:04:17.975 --> 00:04:20.294
say that grace is open to you,

104
00:04:20.294 --> 00:04:21.854
no matter who you are,

105
00:04:21.854 --> 00:04:22.955
no matter what you've done,

106
00:04:22.955 --> 00:04:24.095
no matter where you've been,

107
00:04:24.095 --> 00:04:26.374
no matter what your circumstances are,

108
00:04:26.374 --> 00:04:27.895
grace is open to you.

109
00:04:27.895 --> 00:04:30.394
And furthermore, there isn't anything

110
00:04:30.394 --> 00:04:33.695
